            .row
              .col-md-12
                - if Interest.find_by(user_id: current_user.id, category: "Mortgage")
                  %p 
                    At this time, we don’t offer mortgage options, however, we are planning to offer this soon. You've already indicated your interest, so we'll notify you when mortgage options become available.
